        a                        fabio:Figure ;
        dc:description           "Figures 6. Fore and hind wing of Rodrigama gauldi sp. n. (paratype) (scale: 2 mm)." , "Figures 4 - 15. Scanning electron micrographs of Rodrigama gauldi sp. n. (paratype). 4 Head, posterior aspect 5 head, postero-lateral aspect 6 clypeus, malar space and mandible, anterior aspect 7 anterior part of mesosoma, lateral aspect 8 propodeum, dorsal aspect; 9 - 10 fore tibia 9 dorsal aspect 10 stout spines distal end; 11 - 12 first metasomal tergite 11 lateral aspect 12 dorsal aspect 13 second metasomal tergite, dorsal aspect 14 posterior end of metasoma, lateral aspect 15 ovipositor tip, lateral aspect (scale: 0.1 mm for 9, 10; 0.5 mm for 4 - 8, 13, 15; 1.0 mm for 11, 12, 14)." , "Figures 17 - 20. Scanning electron micrographs of Rodrigama takakuwai (holotype). 17 Anterior part of mesosoma, lateral aspect 18 propodeum, dorsal aspect 19 first metasomal tergite, dorsal aspect 20 second metasomal tergite, dorsal aspect. (scale: 0.5 mm for 18, 20; 1.0 mm for 17, 19)." , "Figures 1 - 3. Rodrigama spp., whole insect, lateral aspect. 1 Rodrigama gauldi sp. n. (holotype) 2 Rodrigama takakuwai sp. n. (holotype) 3 Rodrigama gamezi Gauld (paratype) (scale: 10 mm)." ;
